---
title: Deluxe Lamb Shoulder & Parmesan Pie with Filo Pastry & Balsamic Green Bean Rocket Salad
description: For tonight’s dinner, we’ve done the hard bit for you by slow cooking lamb shoulder to meltingly tender perfection. This forms
the base of our favourite cold-weather meal - a hearty, soul-satiating pie. Top the lamb filling with layers of flaky filo and a
sprinkling of Parmesan for the ultimate demonstration of stylish comfort food.
